    "Name": "Grand Dragon",
    "Details": "Sorenson's Sabres member Emory Wilk's Dragon was among the earliest new-tech \"Grand\" upgrades in the lead-up to the War of 3039. It was rebuilt with less refined bulkier Endo Steel chassis and 3039 era double strength heat sinks, retaining only the medium laser and carrying a prototype ER Large Laser and LRM-15 with two tons of reloads as its main weapons.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Stable</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.13</color></b>",
